::: {#96df67b9 .cell execution_count=15}
``` {.python .cell-code}
(clean_fuels
    .filter(
        pl.col("region")=="Europe",
        pl.col("year")==2022,
        pl.col("prop_clean_fuels_cooking_pct")<50
        )
)
```

